	   <tr><td colspan=2>Heh, while there are rumors of Armor-summoning spells in the upcoming release, there are currently none in play. Your Phantom Leather spell is a self-only HP/AC buff that costs a cats-eye Agate per casting. It is invaluable when soloing as it also has a regeneration component that speeds recovery from pulls gone awry.<br><br>Thayn<br>&nbsp;<br>Zaloren V'Shnev<br>Enchanter of Innoruuk<br>Master Jeweler<br>Journeyman Smith<br>Vazaelle</td></tr>
