2 seconds i would rather have a earth pets 6 second root hit then waiting an extra 6 seconds for the pet to save my ass on a bad nuke/pull or a heavy nuke from a fire pet<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>Fire Solo/Group<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>Solo<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>1. Its heavy DS(Taunt)Nuke Can make swift work of most enemys<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>Group<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>1. its DD can do some nice damage and its DS can hurt alot if its geting hit by something it can take on pretty well<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>WANRING: The fire pet cannot provide the group with an extra tank<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>Always keep your DS and BO spells on pet at all time 20+<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>Also make sure your earth pets root sticks a few times if it barly does use or not at all use your water pet<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>--------------------------------------------------<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
